flowchart TB
    A([Start]) --> B[Open Transaction Entry Form]
    B --> C[Enter Transaction Details]
    C --> D[Submit Transaction]

    D --> E{Required Fields Valid?}
    E -- No --> F[Display Validation Errors]
    F --> C

    E -- Yes --> G[Create Transaction Object]
    G --> H[Send to Application Services]
    H --> I[Process Transaction]
    I --> J[Update Budget/Goal Data]
    J --> K[Persist Transaction]
    K --> L[Refresh Dashboard and Summaries]
    L --> M[Display Confirmation]
    M --> N([End])